<strong class="selflink">Thermopylae</strong> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Artemisium" title="Battle of Artemisium">Artemisium</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Salamis" title="Battle of Salamis">Salamis</a> – <a href="/wiki/Second_Persian_invasion_of_Greece#Siege_of_Potidea" title="Second Persian invasion of Greece">Potidea</a> – <a href="/wiki/Second_Persian_invasion_of_Greece#Siege_of_Olynthus" title="Second Persian invasion of Greece">Olynthus</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Plataea" title="Battle of Plataea">Plataea</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Mycale" title="Battle of Mycale">Mycale</a><br /></p>
